@Jordan2386 your GPU is old enough that it has a CUDA Capability < 3.0.
The pytorch binaries dont support it, but if you build from source it might work.
However, we dont support or recommend using the GPU on this card, as it will likely be slower than and has no benefits compared to using the CPU.
